README:
archinstall_helper:
this is a step by step install guide for archlinux.
It should assist especially archlinux beginners which haven't installed
a linux system on commandline yet.
Guide means that the user can open a help
for every of the installation steps
and look up what he has to do next.



Installing:
via makefile and DESTDIR=/usr or whatever

Using:
Enter ai-helper and go step by step through
a installation of archlinux